Entries.default: "Did you catch the new play by the Pegleg Performers yet? It's awful."
"'The Green Menace?' That I did. Made me want to poke out my eyes."
"I'm telling you, ask for Irwena in the King's Coffin. She'll make you see stars!"
"You half-masted sot! She's got to be ninety years old."
"Heard you tried to 'borrow' an artifact from the Treasure Trove. How's the arm?"
"You're lucky to be alive. Dimesa's not usually so forgiving."
